# ── AI Style Advisor ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Required for the ✦ AI tab.
# Calls claude-sonnet-4-6 directly from the browser (CORS header required).
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com
VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Optional: override the Anthropic API endpoint.
# Default: https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages
# VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_URL=https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages


# ── HD Try-On (CatVTON) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Optional: Hugging Face access token for higher rate limits on the Space.
# Without a token the Space is still usable but may be rate-limited or
# unavailable during high-traffic periods.
# Get one at https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens (read role is enough)
VITE_HF_TOKEN=hf_...

# Optional: HF Space slug for HD try-on.
# Default: zhengchong/CatVTON
# Change this to self-host or use an alternative try-on Space, e.g.:
#   Nymbo/Virtual-Try-On
#   franciszzj/Leffa
# VITE_CATVTON_SPACE=zhengchong/CatVTON


# ── Notes ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# All VITE_* variables are bundled into the client at build time.
# Do not commit a filled .env to version control — keep secrets in .env only.
# For a production deployment use a backend proxy to keep API keys server-side.
